  <!-- WHAT I DON'T DO -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8 reveal">
          <div class="text-center mb-4">
            <span class="section-label justify-content-center"><span class="dot"></span> Boundaries</span>
            <h2 class="section-title">What I <span style="color:#ef4444;">Don't</span> Do</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="dont-do-section">
            <ul>
              <li><i class="fas fa-times-circle"></i> WordPress themes or plugin customization</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-times-circle"></i> Copy-paste template work with no real engineering</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-times-circle"></i> "Can you do it for free / exposure?" projects</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-times-circle"></i> Rush jobs with unrealistic 24-hour deadlines</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-times-circle"></i> Unethical software (scrapers, spam bots, etc.)</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-times-circle"></i> Graphic design, video editing, or content writing</li>
            </ul>
            <p style="margin-top:20px; color:var(--text-muted); font-size:0.88rem; text-align:center;">
              I focus on what I'm exceptional at. This ensures every client gets my absolute best work.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="section bg-dark-2" style="border-top:1px solid var(--glass-border);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
          <div class="text-center mb-5 reveal">
            <span class="section-label justify-content-center"><span class="dot"></span> FAQ</span>
            <h2 class="section-title">Common <span class="gradient-text">Questions</span></h2>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion faq-accordion reveal" id="faqAccordion">

            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq1">
                What is your typical project timeline?
              </button></h2>
              <div id="faq1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  It depends on scope. A basic website takes 1-2 weeks. A full-stack application with backend, database, and authentication takes 3-6 weeks. Enterprise projects (SaaS/MVP) typically require 2-4 months. I'll provide a detailed timeline before we start.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq2">
                Do you offer ongoing maintenance and support?
              </button></h2>
              <div id="faq2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  Yes! The Enterprise plan includes 3 months of free maintenance. For other plans, I offer maintenance packages starting at $200/month covering bug fixes, updates, and minor feature additions.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq3">
                What's your payment structure?
              </button></h2>
              <div id="faq3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  I typically work with a 40% upfront deposit, 30% at midpoint milestone, and 30% upon final delivery. For larger projects, we can discuss custom milestone-based payment schedules that work for both of us.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq4">
                Can you work with my existing codebase?
              </button></h2>
              <div id="faq4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  Absolutely. I'm experienced in reading, understanding, and extending existing codebases. I'll start with a code audit to assess quality and architecture, then provide a plan for improvements or feature additions.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq5">
                How do we communicate during the project?
              </button></h2>
              <div id="faq5" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  I'm flexible — Slack, Discord, Email, or Google Meet. I provide weekly progress updates with demos, and I'm available for quick questions during business hours. Transparency is non-negotiable in my process.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

